<collectingCountry id="E28F7623FFFDFFA4FC44FB76FC7934C4" box="[917,991,1188,1221]" name="Chile" pageId="3" pageNumber="496">Chile</collectingCountry>
.” Modified by G. R. Water house in 1839 based on C. Darwin’s restriction of “near old village of Aconcagua [= Plaza Vieja, ca. 
